cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for language transfer. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of transfer learning, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the use of parsing techniques, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
